Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.77,0:02:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard? It showed up again last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.68,0:02:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fifth time. Now at sophomores.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And already 4th victim in this month, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh... They say it's some kind of robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.15,0:02:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's witnesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's something interesting in our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:02:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Moreover, this "something" is a very powerful combat mech.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it's always ready for action!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:05.03,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\pos(191,50)}Enhanced exoskeleton suite on basis of O-Parts technology:\NOMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.14,0:05:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you did that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are thinking about others, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to have friends!!
